description.en:
There are over 400 million individuals in the world with a diabetic diagnosis. Throughout the
years, new treatments have been developed through the power of research, science, and
medicine. However, there are many that still suffer from this disease, and it’s time to be the change.

Why Gummy Beans?
This crypto space as a whole has changed. People have began to lose trust in investing their
money into crypto. With all the scams, “rug pulls”, and “honey pots”, many have lost money. We want to be the change in this space. We want to be the role models by presenting a token with full transparency. A community that can make a difference in this space and be a part of the revolution to find a cure for Diabetes
